data.description: PRICE ADJUSTED FOR QUICK SALE!! This Fabulous River-Front POOL Home is a must-see in Tampa!! NO HOA OR CDDs.  This immaculate completely remodeled 4 bed, 3 ½ bath home has too much to offer.  This fantastic floorplan starts with a full in-law suite/studio apartment on the ground level, a full bath, and a separate entrance. The first floor of the home offers multiple views of the Hillsborough River that can be seen through the large picture windows of the family room,  and from the outside front and side porches.  When walking through the first-floor entrance, you will step into a foyer with a finished terrazzo flooring inlay and stairs to the 2nd floor on your right. Facing straight from this entrance, you will step into the formal living area. For those relaxing moments, you can enjoy your living room by cozying up to your fireplace overlooking the pool.  To the left of the entrance is the family room that overlooks the Hillsborough River. It has a natural flow into the Eat-In Kitchen. The kitchen is a true chef’s delight, as it features stainless steel appliances, a built-in microwave wall oven combo, an abundance of cabinetry, granite countertops, and an island with a cooktop,  A large pantry room/laundry room combination can be found just off of the kitchen.  Right beside the kitchen is the formal Dining. There is an additional seating area with a storage room across from the formal dining that leads out onto the private backyard which boasts a sparkling swimming pool. The backyard is accessible for storing your boat or other toys through a double gate, which is ideal with the Riverhills Boat Ramp & Park on the Hillsborough River just 1/2 block away.   Explore the upstairs and discover generously sized secondary bedrooms to the right that overlook the Hillsborough River, and the 3rd bedroom has a view of the pool and a large bathroom with double sinks. Your primary master bedroom suite is located on the 2nd floor as well, featuring views of the pool, his and her vanities, a walk-in shower, and a ginormous walk-in closet.   The second floor has a hardwood floor throughout.  There are many community amenities nearby, including the Temple Terrace Golf & Country Club, as well as the Riverhills Pickleball Courts, Riverside Park, and Biltmore Park. FLEXIBILITY IS KEY in this fabulous home - so many options are available with this floorplan, it offers something for everyone! You need to tour this extraordinary property and area in person!  Additional highlights of this home are a Water Heated Sept. 2022. Sewer Reline, and PVC outside July 2023. Pex repiped the entire house Sept. 2022. Backhouse gutters July 2022.  New Pool Pump 2022 and Resurfaced 9/2023. Mostly new Windows and Patio door. Pest Control Service paid for the full year. FURNITURE NOT INCLUDED BUT, NEGOTIABLE.  Room measurements are approximate. All information is deemed accurate but must be verified by the buyer and buyer's agent.
